    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >12个全新专属随从，全新专属羁绊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新角色「德科蒂妮」拥有12个全新随从，包含治疗、魔法、战士、射手、护盾等多种职业，更多全新专属羁绊「帝国」，与其他羁绊组合成不同流派和各具特色的阵容体系。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新角色同样适用于【无尽模式】以及【混沌之路】两种模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025130/extras/7c31b3567a9c400be6b81fe25f0e8327.poster.avif?t=1742463615\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025130/extras/7c31b3567a9c400be6b81fe25f0e8327.webm?t=1742463615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025130/extras/7c31b3567a9c400be6b81fe25f0e8327.mp4?t=1742463615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新的随从装备，更强力的援助</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据全新随从所搭配的全新专属装备，让随从有更强的属性，也有对应的羁绊装备，让阵容更快成型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025130/extras/908d6fcc690f104dbbd278c5f658081d.poster.avif?t=1742463615\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025130/extras/908d6fcc690f104dbbd278c5f658081d.webm?t=1742463615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025130/extras/908d6fcc690f104dbbd278c5f658081d.mp4?t=1742463615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁新元素魔法牌，冰冻敌军</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新角色「德科蒂妮」出身于尤加帝国，擅长使用冰冻的魔法攻击，全新的魔法牌动效和效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025130/extras/2daf4a1eda809cd0af3f91ab742e58ca.poster.avif?t=1742463615\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025130/extras/2daf4a1eda809cd0af3f91ab742e58ca.webm?t=1742463615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025130/extras/2daf4a1eda809cd0af3f91ab742e58ca.mp4?t=1742463615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4段全新剧情，不同搭配产生不同的剧情结局</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此次更新依旧保持正式版角色之间搭配不同剧情的设定，德科蒂妮分别与莱丝丽、荷莉、飞鸟以及神去有不一样的剧情和分支结局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025130/extras/271f793886ecd26927a61a1061ff340d.poster.avif?t=1742463615\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025130/extras/271f793886ecd26927a61a1061ff340d.webm?t=1742463615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025130/extras/271f793886ecd26927a61a1061ff340d.mp4?t=1742463615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
